                            1. Perfect Model Performance: All three models achieved 100% accuracy, indicating strong predictive signals in the data
                            2. Risk Category Dominance: The risk_category feature alone accounts for nearly 59% of prediction power
                            3. Drug-Related Features: Drug information (drug_name + ndc_code) contributes ~19% to predictions
                            4. Financial Indicators: Claim amount is a significant predictor of FWA
                            5. Model Efficiency: All models trained in under 1 second, suitable for real-time deployment

                            For Production Deployment

                            1. Model Selection: Deploy Random Forest for robustness and interpretability
